1 - Download the repository

2 - Edit the config.php file

3 - Edit the database.php file (default: $db['default']['database'] = 'admin_base';)

4 - Create database "admin_base" with SQL script db.sql.txt

5 - Add your use to the database (password should be MD5)

6 - Acess your backend at: yourbaseurl.com/index.php/admin/login

7 - Have fun! =)